  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "Pokémon Card Game: Asobikata DS is a game which focuses on teaching players how to play the Pokémon Trading Card Game. The Beginning Set was rereleased on August 5, 2011, which contained the same cards as the September 2010 Beginning Set, but came with this game.\n\nIt has tutorials and a digital rulebook. After the player has completed all the tutorials, there are five different CPU characters to play against.",
